  "detailed_description": "<h1>ACCOLADES</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/694090/extras/285e1f05f65230fe5f73ab37efb7ddf5.avif?t=1733839694\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into <strong>Apex Construct</strong>, the original VR action-adventure classic. Discover intense archery combat and a gripping story in an award-winning single-player campaign.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Experience The VR Classic</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/694090/extras/24156a91fb9167f1ccba3a17755ca456.poster.avif?t=1733839694\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/694090/extras/24156a91fb9167f1ccba3a17755ca456.webm?t=1733839694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/694090/extras/24156a91fb9167f1ccba3a17755ca456.mp4?t=1733839694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Awaken in a stunning post-apocalyptic world. Grab your bow and uncover the mystery behind two warring AI entities. Battle against powerful mechanical enemies, and explore the rustic remains of a civilization lost to time. Upgrade your gear, hunt for collectibles, and prepare to ask yourself: who can you trust?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full 7+ hour single-player narrative campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deep action system with authentic bow combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete in leaderboards in the challenge-driven Cygnia Cup</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Specific graphics enhancements to make the most of Quest 3, 2, and 1</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/694090/extras/117503f1a7fe5da6109a919cc115710e.poster.avif?t=1733839694\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/694090/extras/117503f1a7fe5da6109a919cc115710e.webm?t=1733839694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/694090/extras/117503f1a7fe5da6109a919cc115710e.mp4?t=1733839694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into <strong>Apex Construct</strong>, the original VR action-adventure classic. Discover intense archery combat and a gripping story in an award-winning single-player campaign.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Experience The VR Classic</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/694090/extras/24156a91fb9167f1ccba3a17755ca456.poster.avif?t=1733839694\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/694090/extras/24156a91fb9167f1ccba3a17755ca456.webm?t=1733839694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/694090/extras/24156a91fb9167f1ccba3a17755ca456.mp4?t=1733839694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Awaken in a stunning post-apocalyptic world. Grab your bow and uncover the mystery behind two warring AI entities. Battle against powerful mechanical enemies, and explore the rustic remains of a civilization lost to time. Upgrade your gear, hunt for collectibles, and prepare to ask yourself: who can you trust?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full 7+ hour single-player narrative campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deep action system with authentic bow combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete in leaderboards in the challenge-driven Cygnia Cup</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Specific graphics enhancements to make the most of Quest 3, 2, and 1</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/694090/extras/117503f1a7fe5da6109a919cc115710e.poster.avif?t=1733839694\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/694090/extras/117503f1a7fe5da6109a919cc115710e.webm?t=1733839694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/694090/extras/117503f1a7fe5da6109a919cc115710e.mp4?t=1733839694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
